{"text_id":54552,"tokens":["Device","-","to","-","device"," (","D","2","D",")"," communication"," under","laying"," cellular"," networks"," allows"," mobile"," devices"," such"," as"," smartphones"," and"," tablets"," to"," use"," the"," licensed"," spectrum"," allocated"," to"," cellular"," services"," for"," direct"," peer","-","to","-","peer"," transmission","."," D","2","D"," communication"," can"," be"," implemented"," either"," as"," an"," overlay"," solution"," or"," an"," under","lay"," solution","."," The"," latter"," allows"," direct"," D","2","D"," links"," to"," be"," established"," without"," interference"," with"," existing"," cellular"," communications","."," In"," the"," present"," work",","," we"," compare"," the"," performance"," of"," D","2","D"," communication"," under","laying"," a"," macro","cellular"," LTE"," system"," with"," that"," of"," an"," under","laying"," system"," based"," on"," a"," small"," cell"," network","."," Using"," stochastic"," geometry",","," we"," calculate"," the"," outage"," probability"," and"," throughput"," of"," D","2","D"," communication"," as"," functions"," of"," distance",","," cell"," radius",","," and"," D","2","D"," user"," density","."," The"," throughput"," of"," the"," under","laying"," D","2","D"," system"," is"," always"," lower"," than"," that"," of"," the"," overlay"," system"," due"," to"," limited"," spatial"," reuse"," of"," the"," spectrum","."," The"," results"," show"," that"," the"," performance"," gap"," between"," the"," two"," systems"," is"," small"," for"," distances"," larger"," than"," ","1","0","0"," m",","," thus"," indicating"," the"," feasibility"," of"," using"," the"," overlay"," system"," in"," urban"," scenarios","."," In"," this"," paper",","," we"," consider"," a"," two","-","user"," down","link"," system"," with"," two","-","tier"," relay","ing"," and"," non","cooperative"," relay"," selection","."," Two"," communication"," modes",","," direct"," mode"," and"," relay"," mode","